<item>
            <title>[LU-12205] host_nids_address() fix for MR setup</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12205</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lnet-seltftest.sh fails on MR setup because of host_nids_address()  defect.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example:&lt;br/&gt;
With MR setup we have:&lt;br/&gt;
lctl list_nids&lt;br/&gt;
192.168.101.3@tcp&lt;br/&gt;
10.0.101.3@tcp1&lt;br/&gt;
10.0.201.3@tcp2&lt;br/&gt;
For NETTYPE=tcp host_nids_address() should give the result&lt;br/&gt;
192.168.101.3 only.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
